Name:
* CHN disqualified from the competition as one member of the team (Dong Fangxiao) was too young to compete at the Sydney Olympics. 




Women's Team - Gymnastics - Sydney 2000 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     First step in the gymnastics competition was the team competition/qualifying round in which all entrants performed optional exercises on all apparatuses. Seven gymnasts were allowed in each team and the team could choose six to compete on each apparatus. Top five scores per team on each exercise counted in the team score. Event facts: Women's Team competition was held at the Sydney SuperDome, Olympic Park and 6  teams participated in the event. 





These results for Women's Team - Sydney 2000 Summer Olympics - are based on the official olympic reports and the Olympian Database
